{"tid":268093,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友幫女朋友放貓，掛住屙屎佢走失左。","createTime":"2017-06-02T18:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T07:58:42.000Z","uid":93286,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b405ab9776bd387fb0ea701045018d1fd8a444cf","tid":268093,"uid":93286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"我唔知呢個藉口有幾咁荒謬，<br />\n我唔知係真定假嘅，<br />\n就當佢係真嘅先，<br />\n呢個人一直都唔肯公開佢個Facebook post，<br />\n令到一班想分享呢一個唔見貓訊息嘅朋友，<br />\n冇辦法令到佢哋嘅資料，<br />\n迫於無奈想大家一齊幫手搵下隻貓。<br />\n以下係一啲資料<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/015814_375a0ffef5fb2ad66a75d6ed7c27fb04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F015814_375a0ffef5fb2ad66a75d6ed7c27fb04.jpg&h=bde54179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/015818_b874311e948b594230173c05953f27e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F015818_b874311e948b594230173c05953f27e7.jpg&h=568549c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/015820_6e6353d66c21f6e81cf7633d57166659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F015820_6e6353d66c21f6e81cf7633d57166659.jpg&h=028012ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/015821_0a60700700e013dc337838474a480721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F015821_0a60700700e013dc337838474a480721.jpg&h=cc628e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個女仔去咗旅行個男朋友幫佢照顧貓，<br />\n點知因為男朋友要屙屎，<br />\n所以隻貓走失左，<br />\n根據佢嘅資料，<br />\n咁啱咁得咁橋街上傾盆大雨，<br />\n我唔知去邊句真邊句假，<br />\n所以大家如果想知道佢貓係邊度唔見，<br />\n可以打去問吓上面個電話，<br />\n了解下睇吓幫唔幫到佢搵隻貓，<br />\n我相信佢咁愛&quot;貓&quot;，<br />\n佢聲稱而家凌晨兩點佢依然搵緊，<br />\n佢唔會介意你為咗佢隻貓而打俾佢，<br />\n其實係真心想大家幫佢搵返隻貓嘅，<br />\n大家即管打俾佢問佢拎多啲資料啦。"},{"pid":"b3255a8ade1dfcd48b8d3809fd34110538e5d4c9","tid":268093,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:06:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a04a754b25a48a35f74e3dfe11dc26d19e4748e","tid":268093,"uid":93286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"個男仔仲要話落雨啲水會令到佢眼鏡模糊，<br />\n所以好難搵隻貓，<br />\n隻貓得幾個月大嘅咋，<br />\n希望你哋可以搵隻貓啦，<br />\n貓同人一樣都有生命，<br />\n珍惜係必須，<br />\n佢竟然為咗屙屎，<br />\n而唔理一隻幾個月大嘅貓，<br />\n真係無言以對。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/03/020635_d6f43605b34927aaa4d6dfc1c23a091d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F03%2F020635_d6f43605b34927aaa4d6dfc1c23a091d.jpg&h=dc433ad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f47a172272fa1e1908e5f7269ce1ab6f0011ad5c","tid":268093,"uid":9435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個Mun Lui做乜撚</blockquote><br />\n同感 <br />\n做乜鳩 <br />\n關佢撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee284bdc721c6bd9c85d650c19bd29e6e7ebf12","tid":268093,"uid":9435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:10:02.000Z","msg":"如果樓主係放上黎公審 <br />\n我會直接block 撚左你個on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ed4acf98672177b6bf3621d1ab3f0cd7679257","tid":268093,"uid":93286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個Mun Lui做乜撚</blockquote><br />\n個Mun Lui只係一個想叫佢公開個post想幫手share既人，但又俾佢屌翻轉頭。"},{"pid":"f4564b4949513315a08b92985c1e3d7c89e26dde","tid":268093,"uid":93286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果樓主係放上黎公審 <br />\n我會直接block 撚左你個on9仔<img src=\"/